{"tid":2377903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳文敏：引入《國安法》違憲","createTime":"2021-01-24T04:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T06:24:52.000Z","uid":261647,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"206ff998c349a75be822ba8db81657c796339626","tid":2377903,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:23:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10153164619922448/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10153164619922448%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Taj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=677b0959\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10153164619922448/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fEurN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fEurN5.jpg&h=bf64df3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《國家安全法》引入《基本法》附件，在香港實施。香港大學法律學院教授陳文敏昨日表明反對，直指做法違憲，因《基本法》「係冇空間畀國家立法」。<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏表示，當年草擬《基本法》時，已經排除將《國安法》引入香港，直指吳秋北「唔係好熟《基本法》」。陳指本港普通法涵蓋範圍甚廣，唯一沒有的是「以言入罪」。他強調，引入《國安法》反會引起法院審理問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏指大學討論不應避開一些具爭議的議題，並要有客觀分析及獨立思考，這正正是大學應做的事情。他很高興學生做到這種事情，「一定要有很多不同思潮，如果呢啲唔講得嗰啲唔講得，離經叛道，地球係圓嘅唔可以講，就會扼殺思維」。"},{"pid":"6c84d8ebbdee7223aec1f27e46d0788b6c56296a","tid":2377903,"uid":31389,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"咁...又點?"},{"pid":"e5bfa63018fef6d6b77499677231c5b81387fdda","tid":2377903,"uid":48362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"釋法咪得囉<br />\n到時柒閪又奶到成面精 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a39a060573dc34c618ea25b17c7801776e54e4","t